enUS:
- Upgrading will lead to increased equipment requirements.
- There is a +5 modifier to the base level req when upgrading normal -> exceptional.
- There is a +7 modifier to the base level req when upgrading exceptional -> elite.
zhTW:
- 升級將導致裝備需求增加.
- 當一件裝備從 普通級 升級為 擴展級 基礎需求等級+5
- 當一件裝備從 擴展級 升級為 精英級 基礎需求等級+7.
